Firebase Devslopes

-Firebase Auth
-Firebase DB:
	It is real time database.[CRUD](where we can store all the data)
-Firebase Storage
	-This is where user can upload files and things like that.
	-Let say when user submit image through the app, It can be stored in Firebase storage. 
	-And we can access at later point of time.


>>Realtime Database Rules<<
============================
Inorder to perform database operation, security rules require users to be authenticated.


